node.text:
Jumbo Flour Tortilla, Abuelita’s Rice, Black Beans, Chorizo (Vegan), Yuba Carnitas (Vegan), Fried Plantains, Jalapeños, Onion, Shredded Lettuce, Maldita Sauce, Garlic Aioli, Creamy Green Salsa! 🇲🇽🔥 I’m NOT Vegan and this burrito was delicious!
📍: Charly’s Vegan Tacos
🌇: Miami, FL
🎥: @foodyfetish #foodyfetishoriginal
Tag a Hungry Friend!👇🏼

node.text:
Morning Coffee with a VIEW from the “Royal Suite” at @stregisbalharbour! ☕️🌅

Swipe Left to see the spectacular sunrise, beach views, and suite. This hotel is on another level!

📍: @stregisbalharbour
🌇: Bal Harbour, FL
🎥: @foodyfetish #foodyfetishoriginal
